title: MIHA PRAJS
text:
I’m Miha, a 19-year-old guy from Slovenia. I’m currently studying Bioinformatics at University of Primorska. Previously I gained expirenece in microbiology, biotechnology and chemistry laboratory as a part of school work in High School. I also worked in laboratory A2 Análises Químicas for three weeks in Portugal as a part of Erasmus+ exchange.



University of Primorska, Faculty of Mathematics, Natural Science and Informations Technologies.  Programme: Bioinformatics, academic, 1st Bologne cycle  From 2023 - current. famnit.upr.si/   Biotehniški izobraževalni center Ljubljana, Gimnazija in veterinarka šola.
